    <h1>Accessibility</h1>
<br />
<p>
This website has been generated with <a target="_blank" href="https://www.upc.edu/comunicacio/www/genweb-upc"><strong>Genweb UPC v3 
<img alt="(open in new window)" src="icon_blank.gif" class="link_blank"></strong></a>, a tool that allows to the creation and management of web pages according to the UPC institutional style guide.
<br /><br />

<a target="_blank" href="https://www.upc.edu/comunicacio/www/genweb-upc"><strong>Genweb UPC v3 <img alt="(open in new window)" 
src="icon_blank.gif" class="link_blank"></strong></a> is a project co-authored by the <a target="_blank" href="http://www.upc.edu/comunicacio">
Comunication and Promotion Service <img alt="(open in new window)" src="icon_blank.gif" class="link_blank"></a> of UPC and <a target="_blank" 
href="http://www.upcnet.es">UPCnet <img alt="(open in new window)" src="icon_blank.gif" class="link_blank"></a> developed with the Open Source 
